        <h2>Disabling Xbox Game Bar</h2>
        <p>In this guide I'm gonna go over how to disable the game bar</p>
        <p>At the bottom of the page there is a short explanation on what it is and why you should disable it.</p>
        <div class="row-dotted-line"></div>

        <h3>1. Get to your settings</h3>
        
        <div class="ul-box">
            <ul>
                <li>Click your WIN key, it will pull up your start menu.</li>
                <li>On the start menu you will see a cog/gear icon click it to get to the settings.</li>
                <li>When you're in the settings menu click on the gaming section.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="img-flexbox">
