        </div>

        <div class="row-dotted-line"></div>

        <h3>2. Turning off Xbox game bar</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>On the left side-menu make sure you're on the Xbox Game Bar section.</li>
            <li>On the right side you'll see a on/off switch. You want to turn it off.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="img-flexbox">
            <%= image_tag "GBsettings2.png", class: "flexbox-ite"%>
        </div>

        <div class="row-dotted-line"></div>

        <p>
            You're all set. Game bar is now off.
        </p>

